[I] C library for simpler use of LV2 plugins

[T] Lilv is a C library (with Python bindings) for simple use of LV2 plugins in
[T] applications, which includes utilities for investigating installed LV2
[T] plugins. Lilv is the successor to SLV2, rewritten to be significantly
[T] faster and have minimal dependencies.

[U] https://drobilla.net/software/lilv.html

